name: Uaena Game
description:
WASD to move, mouse to aim and shoot.

Turn the milks into starcandies, and collect them to gain points.

Once in a awhile, Miss Tweety will turn up, go give her a hug and see what happens! She has a busy schedule, so she'll disappear quickly, so be fast!

Oh don't get hit by the milks too.

I don't own any of the graphics or music.
